‘What is the Purpose of Our Life?’, Hampstead,
1.11.1983

00:00:07.110 --> 00:00:11.099
Key Words and Phrases:
Purpose of life

00:00:11.099 --> 00:00:12.240
confusion
government

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:16.230
norms/titles
political systems fail us (democracy, demonocracy,

00:00:16.230 --> 00:00:19.080
communism)
Mother Earth and biological sustainers

00:00:19.080 --> 00:00:21.029
living all-pervading force
Kundalini

00:00:21.029 --> 00:00:24.449
Kali Yuga/Krita Yuga
Mohatma Ghandi/Christ – “manly men”

00:00:24.449 --> 00:00:25.449
and compassion
‘born again’

