checking vibrations
the nature of Mother’s work

00:00:41.320 --> 00:00:52.920
General Content:
Science and our mental projections are not

00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:57.109
connected to higher, living force, so they
fail us.

00:00:57.109 --> 00:01:02.929
Biological movement within us is spiral, but
mental projections are linear, dead.

00:01:02.929 --> 00:01:11.520
We must become scientists of the Divine, and
understand the knowledge of the roots.

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:17.120
We are all One; all of God’s children – no
nationalities exist.

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:27.920
You can find information about the Holy Ghost
in the Bible, but you must go to Indian scriptures

00:01:27.920 --> 00:01:29.670
to find information about the ‘Adi Shakti’.

00:01:29.670 --> 00:01:36.130
Doctors must learn about the three sides of
a human: physical, mental and emotional.

00:01:36.130 --> 00:01:39.720
With Sahaja Yoga you can cure yourself and
others.

00:01:39.720 --> 00:01:48.000
You cannot pay for Kundalini rising – if
you could, or did, it would no longer be benevolent.

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:53.620
Question Period Following Talk:
What happens to our Spirit after death?

00:01:53.620 --> 00:01:56.690
Does self-realization interfere with normal
functioning?

00:01:56.690 --> 00:02:01.330
Story of a woman with a serious heart problem.

00:02:01.330 --> 00:02:08.960
Where does depression come from and can Sahaja
Yoga cure it?

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:11.049
Is meditation difficult?

00:02:11.049 --> 00:02:13.790
What is the evidence of Shri Mataji’s own
enlightenment?

00:02:13.790 --> 00:02:16.170
Self-Realization Exercise:
Shri Mataji finishes the talk by giving the

00:02:16.170 --> 00:02:19.260
audience self-realization, and She comments
on left vishuddi guilt problems.

00:02:19.260 --> 00:02:23.500
What is the purpose of our life?

00:02:23.500 --> 00:02:32.290
Is it that the whole evolution is purposeless;
that there is no Divine play in it?

00:02:32.290 --> 00:02:40.159
Then why it was done with such care, and why
we have become human beings?

00:02:40.159 --> 00:02:48.680
So first, we have to come to right conclusions
- that is the counseling you can call it – we

00:02:48.680 --> 00:02:55.790
have come, we have to understand, that we
have not become what we are supposed to be.

00:02:55.790 --> 00:02:58.489
That’s why we are in confusion.

00:02:58.489 --> 00:03:02.549
We do not have answers for these fundamental
questions.

00:03:02.549 --> 00:03:06.609
Some believe in God, some don’t believe
in God.

00:03:06.609 --> 00:03:10.209
Some believe in Christ, some believe in Mohammed.

00:03:10.209 --> 00:03:14.980
Some believe in Krishna, some say that it’s
all science.

00:03:14.980 --> 00:03:17.073
We are so confused, and there is no answer
to it.

00:03:17.073 --> 00:03:21.810
The reason is we are not that what we have
to be.

00:03:21.810 --> 00:03:29.290
Supposing an instrument is given to you, and
you don’t know anything about that.

00:03:29.290 --> 00:03:39.889
Then you don’t know what is the purpose
of that instrument, and for which it was created,

00:03:39.889 --> 00:03:45.120
and to what use it has to be put.

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:49.719
Thus, there’s a confusion, and the confusion
is to such an extent that in that confusion

00:03:49.719 --> 00:03:51.230
we have formed, from ideas, mental projections.

00:03:51.230 --> 00:03:52.879
Artificial, without any biological basis for
it.

00:03:52.879 --> 00:03:54.999
There is no biological basis for our mental
projections.

00:03:54.999 --> 00:04:01.719
Just sit down here, and think now, that see,
this kind of a government if you make, then

00:04:01.719 --> 00:04:03.909
people will be alright.

00:04:03.909 --> 00:04:06.849
This is your own mental projection.

00:04:06.849 --> 00:04:09.569
It has nothing living behind it; it’s all
dead thought.

00:04:09.569 --> 00:04:13.290
By changing the governments, have you been
able to transform the people?

00:04:13.290 --> 00:04:19.959
I have been to Russia, I have been to China,
I have been to America, to all these places.

00:04:19.959 --> 00:04:25.960
Human beings are just the same; there is no
difference whatsoever.

00:04:25.960 --> 00:04:32.110
Maybe some are more honest, some are more
dishonest, some are more immoral, some are

00:04:32.110 --> 00:04:36.360
less immoral, but, on the balance, if you
see you find any kind of person everywhere.

00:04:36.360 --> 00:04:43.530
So one has to understand that this kind of
mental projection that we were having about

00:04:43.530 --> 00:04:48.080
other things like social work, people think
that being social work and all that, our ego

00:04:48.080 --> 00:04:49.080
can be conquered.

00:04:49.080 --> 00:04:50.080
The greatest egoistical people are the social
workers.

00:04:50.080 --> 00:04:51.950
Now these mental projections have created
also lots of norms for us.

00:04:51.950 --> 00:04:54.120
Like, I sit down here and decide I’ll give
a title to someone.

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:55.620
Now he becomes a titlehood.

00:04:55.620 --> 00:05:00.650
Then he’s off, finished, once for all he’s
dead now to anything that is reality because

00:05:00.650 --> 00:05:03.540
he’s living with something so unreal, which
was given to him by somebody which is so unreal.

00:05:03.540 --> 00:05:04.540
There’s nothing living force behind it.

00:05:04.540 --> 00:05:10.590
Have you seen any man changing by getting
some sort of a title or lot of money?

00:05:10.590 --> 00:05:13.980
On the contrary he becomes worse, never improves.

00:05:13.980 --> 00:05:15.620
So what is the reason?

00:05:15.620 --> 00:05:25.240
Why is it that when we go into an enterprise
of this kind, why is it, we find, that everything

00:05:25.240 --> 00:05:26.240
fails?

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:28.790
You talk of democracy, it becomes demonocracy.

00:05:28.790 --> 00:05:33.230
You talk of communism, you find it is another
headache.

00:05:33.230 --> 00:05:40.280
You talk of anything, it all becomes such
a funny thing, and it recoils back (to you?).

00:05:40.280 --> 00:05:42.440
Whatever you try, any enterprise, it recoils
back.

00:05:42.440 --> 00:05:48.620
Science, what is science now has become nothing
but atomic war.

00:05:48.620 --> 00:05:55.000
How is it science (wandered/wanted/come?)
into atomic war no one knows, but suddenly

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:59.010
it has become a great threat to the whole
world.

00:05:59.010 --> 00:06:00.420
Computers, tomorrow computers will start dominating
us.

00:06:00.420 --> 00:06:06.350
We see those things clearly happening to us,
and we are worried, we are shocked.

00:06:06.350 --> 00:06:17.990
(But/Well?) we don’t know why is it whatever
we try to do, why, it recoils on us, and entangles

00:06:17.990 --> 00:06:20.130
us, and enslaves us.

00:06:20.130 --> 00:06:26.010
The reason is it’s, it has no living force
behind it.

00:06:26.010 --> 00:06:31.830
It’s only mental, at mental level, and human
beings live only on mental level.

00:06:31.830 --> 00:06:39.860
So there has to be another higher level which
is generated when you get in contact with

00:06:39.860 --> 00:06:40.880
a living force.

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:44.270
Now let us see what is that living force.

00:06:44.270 --> 00:06:47.610
The living force is that which sprouts the
seed.

00:06:47.610 --> 00:06:49.180
The Mother earth sprouts the seed.

00:06:49.180 --> 00:06:58.190
If you see the Mother Earth as it is, you
don’t find anything in it, nothing.

00:06:58.190 --> 00:06:59.400
There’s just clay.

00:06:59.400 --> 00:07:06.190
But you put some seed and that wasteful thing
that you think of no use, this mud, that gives

00:07:06.190 --> 00:07:11.140
that life to the seed, and you find that the
flowers become fruits, automatically.

00:07:11.140 --> 00:07:22.690
It’s a wondrous world, if you start looking
at the living work of the living force, because

00:07:22.690 --> 00:07:33.140
we are not in connection with that, whatever
we do, we go into problems, but the nature

00:07:33.140 --> 00:07:36.551
does not, while we do.

00:07:36.551 --> 00:07:39.650
The reason is we have lost our biological
sustainers, or process.

00:07:39.650 --> 00:07:43.680
We are not biologically acting: it’s all
dead action.

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:46.450
What we do is all dead.

00:07:46.450 --> 00:08:01.080
For example, as I told you before also that
something is dead, a tree is dead and you

00:08:01.080 --> 00:08:06.650
make a chair, then you think, ‘I have made
this thing’.

00:08:06.650 --> 00:08:13.490
From dead to dead to dead to dead, and this
dead sits on our head.

00:08:13.490 --> 00:08:18.150
You make a chair, you cannot sit on the ground.

00:08:18.150 --> 00:08:20.620
Then we start another thing like anti-culture
business.

00:08:20.620 --> 00:08:22.180
That also just the same.

00:08:22.180 --> 00:08:24.000
Like pendulum we may move.

00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:27.860
Now, we don’t like democracy, to have communism.

00:08:27.860 --> 00:08:30.780
From communism to democracy, democracy to
communism, there’s no movement!

00:08:30.780 --> 00:08:34.680
Now what is the biological movement, within
us?

00:08:34.680 --> 00:08:44.999
As you know there are peptiles in our body,
and the biological movement of peptiles is

00:08:44.999 --> 00:08:47.910
shown when the movement is spiral.

00:08:47.910 --> 00:08:54.790
When it is spiral then it’s biological,
and when it is linear then it is said that

00:08:54.790 --> 00:08:56.760
they have lost their biological sustainers.

00:08:56.760 --> 00:08:59.050
They have no biological quality in them.

00:08:59.050 --> 00:09:00.370
They have become linear.

00:09:00.370 --> 00:09:05.210
So that sustainers within us, that spiral
movement within us, is existing in our nerves,

00:09:05.210 --> 00:09:07.999
but can become absolutely linear, leading
to death.

00:09:07.999 --> 00:09:17.519
All of our mental projections are linear,
because we cannot with that in our own awareness,

00:09:17.519 --> 00:09:20.910
in our own awareness, jump higher.

00:09:20.910 --> 00:09:23.170
It is so outside.

00:09:23.170 --> 00:09:33.339
For a man might say, think: ‘Ah, I must
try to improve the whole world, I must do

00:09:33.339 --> 00:09:34.470
this thing’.

00:09:34.470 --> 00:09:46.180
There was a gentleman I met who is in charge
of the peace of the world, and the most disturbed

00:09:46.180 --> 00:10:04.180
personality I have ever come across, you see.

00:10:04.180 --> 00:10:42.420
He was jumping this way, he was jumping this
way, every sort of disturbance was in his

00:10:42.420 --> 00:10:51.691
mind, and he’s supposed to be in charge
of the peace of the world; imagine.

00:10:51.691 --> 00:10:52.980
Now what’s the matter with the gentleman?

00:10:52.980 --> 00:11:01.050
Though he thinks of peace, he thinks of such
big things, he talks of higher ideals, everything.

00:11:01.050 --> 00:11:02.949
What is it inside?

00:11:02.949 --> 00:11:05.319
There is nothing, no peace.

00:11:05.319 --> 00:11:07.220
He’s just talking outside.

00:11:07.220 --> 00:11:09.129
What is the reason?

00:11:09.129 --> 00:11:11.230
The reason is it’s only linear.

00:11:11.230 --> 00:11:20.449
He has accepted that he is in charge of the
peace, he must talk of big things, he must

00:11:20.449 --> 00:11:23.019
talk of ideal things, and then the whole thing
drops out.

00:11:23.019 --> 00:11:28.600
We had League of Nations, now we have United
Nations: all flops.

00:11:28.600 --> 00:11:33.649
So to make it spirally activated, what have
we to do?

00:11:33.649 --> 00:11:42.829
First of all we have to come to the right
conclusion, understanding, that whatever we

00:11:42.829 --> 00:11:48.279
have done so far has been linear in its action.

00:11:48.279 --> 00:11:50.019
It’s not biological.

00:11:50.019 --> 00:11:54.100
We cannot transform a flower into a fruit.

00:11:54.100 --> 00:11:57.019
No living action we can take.

00:11:57.019 --> 00:11:59.939
We cannot perform any living action.

00:11:59.939 --> 00:12:10.920
Once we understand that, then we have to know
that we have to become more to be in connection

00:12:10.920 --> 00:12:13.759
with that living force, that all-pervading
force.

00:12:13.759 --> 00:12:18.329
And to get to that all-pervading force, what
have we to do?

00:12:18.329 --> 00:12:21.350
Actually what did we do to become human beings?

00:12:21.350 --> 00:12:22.350
Nothing.

00:12:22.350 --> 00:12:23.350
We just became, spontaneously, Sahaja.

00:12:23.350 --> 00:12:24.350
Sahaj: spontaneously.

00:12:24.350 --> 00:12:30.740
It was just some force within us which worked
it out, that made us human beings.

00:12:30.740 --> 00:12:32.430
We didn’t do anything.

00:12:32.430 --> 00:12:40.439
So one has to understand that if it is a living
process, then you don’t have to do anything

00:12:40.439 --> 00:12:41.439
about it.

00:12:41.439 --> 00:12:42.439
It is effortless.

00:12:42.439 --> 00:12:45.740
This is very difficult for human beings to
understand.

00:12:45.740 --> 00:12:49.751
It is very difficult, because they live with
their ego, and they cannot accept that you

00:12:49.751 --> 00:12:50.751
cannot do it yourself.

00:12:50.751 --> 00:12:54.500
They think, ‘We can do it ourselves’,
which is not possible.

00:12:54.500 --> 00:13:03.529
You have to go to the Mother Earth to ask
the seed to be sprouted.

00:13:03.529 --> 00:13:05.660
You cannot sprout it.

00:13:05.660 --> 00:13:14.200
You may try to dissect it, analyze it, put
it under microscope, but you cannot sprout

00:13:14.200 --> 00:13:15.200
it.

00:13:15.200 --> 00:13:23.620
For sprouting, you have to surrender yourself
to that Mother Earth who does the job.

00:13:23.620 --> 00:13:28.610
To begin with, we have to understand that
we are not capable of doing any living work

00:13:28.610 --> 00:13:29.610
whatsoever.

00:13:29.610 --> 00:13:38.670
Once we have that humility within us, then
we start seeing what can happen to us by which

00:13:38.670 --> 00:13:45.550
we can become the masters of that living force.

00:13:45.550 --> 00:13:52.749
To become something you have not done anything,
and to become higher you don’t have to do

00:13:52.749 --> 00:13:53.749
anything.

00:13:53.749 --> 00:14:00.129
That means there is built in within you the
complete mechanism which is going to work

00:14:00.129 --> 00:14:01.499
it out.

00:14:01.499 --> 00:14:08.699
Now before you I would say it’s like a hypothesis
for you and you have to understand it as a

00:14:08.699 --> 00:14:13.089
scientist would understand; with an open mind,
because this is the science of the Divine.

00:14:13.089 --> 00:14:15.089
It’s not known so far.

00:14:15.089 --> 00:14:28.980
This is the knowledge of the roots, not known
to anyone so far, I can say, but to known

00:14:28.980 --> 00:14:33.410
to some people who have evolved themselves.

00:14:33.410 --> 00:14:42.249
They have gone above that state that is just
mental, and these are the very few people

00:14:42.249 --> 00:14:43.249
who know what it is.

00:14:43.249 --> 00:14:50.579
This knowledge is not of today; is of thousands
of years, but, is not the knowledge of the

00:14:50.579 --> 00:15:00.100
tree, as I told you, which we have, but is
the knowledge of the roots, which we have

00:15:00.100 --> 00:15:01.100
to understand.

00:15:01.100 --> 00:15:05.220
The knowledge of the roots is that within
you is placed the root, is called (Shri Mataji

00:15:05.220 --> 00:15:08.209
speaks aside to the yogis present: ‘Is it
here?

00:15:08.209 --> 00:15:09.209
No, ah.

00:15:09.209 --> 00:15:11.019
Somebody can come up, please.’)

00:15:11.019 --> 00:15:15.399
Here, in the triangular bone is placed the
thing called Kundalini.

00:15:15.399 --> 00:15:17.569
It is a Sanskrit word.

00:15:17.569 --> 00:15:21.569
One should not be so frightened of Sanskrit.

00:15:21.569 --> 00:15:28.399
I was surprised, when I went to America, the
first question they asked me: ‘Why should

00:15:28.399 --> 00:15:32.779
you come and teach us about these things which
were in your country?’

00:15:32.779 --> 00:15:40.850
I said: ‘To Me, it is just the same whether
it is America or India.

00:15:40.850 --> 00:15:49.350
Why did you come to India to teach us about
science?’

00:15:49.350 --> 00:15:51.939
Why this kind of an attitude people have?

00:15:51.939 --> 00:16:14.410
Wherever there is knowledge, a humble person
must go and (see it/seek it?)

00:16:14.410 --> 00:17:30.110
This was discovered about 14 000 years back,
where, in England, I don’t think people

00:17:30.110 --> 00:17:38.779
lived here, in this country.

00:17:38.779 --> 00:17:49.169
So why should anybody feel humiliated?

00:17:49.169 --> 00:17:59.039
When you think you are English, or you are
American, you are wrong.

00:17:59.039 --> 00:18:04.470
You are a human being.

00:18:04.470 --> 00:18:11.900
God never made a world like that.

00:18:11.900 --> 00:18:17.549
We are all one, and everybody has to support
each other.

00:18:17.549 --> 00:18:41.760
Like a flower thinks, I am a flower, a leaf
thinks, I am a leaf, and the roots think they

00:18:41.760 --> 00:18:54.710
are roots, then how the whole tree is going
to manifest, just think?

00:18:54.710 --> 00:19:15.860
We are one, there’s nothing that you are
the tree, and you are the leaf, and you are

00:19:15.860 --> 00:19:17.950
the flower, and we are everything.

00:19:17.950 --> 00:19:32.649
So to think like that if that is another mental
projection we have, that ‘I am this’ and

00:19:32.649 --> 00:19:33.840
‘I am that’.

00:19:33.840 --> 00:19:47.930
You are just a human being, which has been
created by God’s grace, to this level, as

00:19:47.930 --> 00:19:57.160
the most beautiful thing, the epitome, of
His creation.

00:19:57.160 --> 00:20:09.880
I would say that, in the west, there are more
seekers, perhaps, than we have in the east,

00:20:09.880 --> 00:20:16.480
perhaps, but that doesn’t mean that it is
only because it is England, or America, but

00:20:16.480 --> 00:20:24.419
it is only that all over the world God has
this blessing and the message for everyone.

00:20:24.419 --> 00:20:35.820
So first of all we must understand that this
is the knowledge of the roots, and this knowledge

00:20:35.820 --> 00:20:44.650
of the roots, unless and until we know about
it, we have no right to criticize it.

00:20:44.650 --> 00:20:51.899
Moreover, by criticizing you are not the gainer,
you are the loser.

00:20:51.899 --> 00:20:59.940
So with complete openness of a student we
have to see to this, that this great force

00:20:59.940 --> 00:21:07.970
is placed within us, in a triangular bone,
whether you are an Australian, American, English,

00:21:07.970 --> 00:21:10.650
Indian, or coming from Timbuctoo.

00:21:10.650 --> 00:21:18.600
All of you, if you are human beings, God has
placed this force within you.

00:21:18.600 --> 00:21:22.010
He doesn’t understand these differences,
actually.

00:21:22.010 --> 00:21:24.850
It’s only we do understand.

00:21:24.850 --> 00:21:35.639
For Him it’s the one world, that beautiful
world He has created, and all the human beings

00:21:35.639 --> 00:21:37.429
are His children.

00:21:37.429 --> 00:21:44.539
So in this triangular bone, is placed this
beautiful thing called the Kundalini, and

00:21:44.539 --> 00:21:48.070
this Kundalini is the motherhood within you.

00:21:48.070 --> 00:21:49.940
It’s a quality.

00:21:49.940 --> 00:21:59.290
It has nothing to do with a woman or a man.

00:21:59.290 --> 00:22:03.390
It’s a quality, is a type, a personality.

00:22:03.390 --> 00:22:10.050
For example, I would say today, Mohatma Ghandi,
people accept him as a great man, because

00:22:10.050 --> 00:22:12.560
he had the quality of compassion.

00:22:12.560 --> 00:22:17.040
He had the quality of giving, of nourishing.

00:22:17.040 --> 00:22:24.320
In the same way all the saints of the world
had this quality.

00:22:24.320 --> 00:22:28.250
They were motherly, full of compassion, love.

00:22:28.250 --> 00:22:30.490
Christ had the same.

00:22:30.490 --> 00:22:39.750
He was so full of compassion that you cannot
call him, in the worldly way, a man, because

00:22:39.750 --> 00:22:45.179
man means he must hate, he must aggress, he
must do all kinds of things to show his ego.

00:22:45.179 --> 00:22:46.179
No.

00:22:46.179 --> 00:22:53.950
He was a personality who had compassion, who
had nourishment.

00:22:53.950 --> 00:22:57.279
Now to become that personality, what have
we to do?

00:22:57.279 --> 00:23:04.770
Again, say I, nothing, because it is all placed
within you.

00:23:04.770 --> 00:23:13.580
The expression of Kundalini within you is
the expression of that great personality.

00:23:13.580 --> 00:23:30.750
When that happens to you, you yourself become
like the Mother Earth, that you can give,

00:23:30.750 --> 00:23:36.600
you can project yourself, that you become
compassion yourself and your compassion acts.

00:23:36.600 --> 00:23:52.269
These days, Kali Yuga is the modern times,
what was the Kali Yuga, the days of confusion,

00:23:52.269 --> 00:24:03.210
is over, and is called as Krita Yuga, means
where this living force will act, and this

00:24:03.210 --> 00:24:08.700
living force has to act through you.

00:24:08.700 --> 00:24:13.360
You become the medium of that living force.

00:24:13.360 --> 00:24:20.020
Actually you become the master of that.

00:24:20.020 --> 00:24:23.710
But the beauty of this is that it manifests
within you also.

00:24:23.710 --> 00:24:30.600
For example, the electricity is flowing through
this; it doesn’t do anything to this instrument.

00:24:30.600 --> 00:24:39.000
But when this force starts flowing through
you, you get completely transformed into a

00:24:39.000 --> 00:24:42.659
new personality, and a personality that Christ
had described that you are to be born again.

00:24:42.659 --> 00:24:44.850
Again, linear way, is that artificially people
can brand themselves ‘born again’.

00:24:44.850 --> 00:24:49.750
But when it happens to you are completely
transformed from within, and the transformation

00:24:49.750 --> 00:24:59.070
is so visible, and so active, as Krita Yuga
has started, that you are amazed.

00:24:59.070 --> 00:25:08.960
You cannot believe, it is fantastic, because
you are fantastically made, extremely fantastically

00:25:08.960 --> 00:25:14.490
made, and that all things starts expressing
itself as soon as it manifests.

00:25:14.490 --> 00:25:21.779
So a human being should know that he’s made
with great care, great love, and for a very

00:25:21.779 --> 00:25:27.549
great thing: is to enjoy the love of his Father.

00:25:27.549 --> 00:25:38.100
When this Kundalini rises within you, passes
through six chakras - the seventh it does

00:25:38.100 --> 00:25:48.710
not cross; the seventh is the guard – then
it creates that spiral movement within our

00:25:48.710 --> 00:25:50.440
awareness.

00:25:50.440 --> 00:25:59.389
The awareness itself gets spirally formed,
and instead of moving in a pendulum you move

00:25:59.389 --> 00:26:06.289
in such a way that you jump higher.

00:26:06.289 --> 00:26:13.250
Your awareness becomes higher than what it
used to be.

00:26:13.250 --> 00:26:15.909
So the human awareness becomes higher.

00:26:15.909 --> 00:26:20.740
There are lots of misunderstandings about
this, and it comes from the ignorance, because

00:26:20.740 --> 00:26:27.600
when you start seeking something from ignorance,
what happens that whatever you find, is a

00:26:27.600 --> 00:26:31.830
partial truth or could be something not the
truth.

00:26:31.830 --> 00:26:39.500
For example, in the darkness, you might see
this and think it’s a snake.

00:26:39.500 --> 00:26:45.640
A wire might look like a snake to you.

00:26:45.640 --> 00:26:47.570
But supposing you suddenly become enlightened.

00:26:47.570 --> 00:26:54.289
Of course, in the beginning, light may not
be that strong.

00:26:54.289 --> 00:26:57.260
In some people it could be little bit, just
a flicker.

00:26:57.260 --> 00:27:15.669
But you start seeing then, and gradually,
if the light improves, and the lantern improves,

00:27:15.669 --> 00:27:20.190
I can say, then you start seeing it, very
clearly, what has gone wrong with you, and

00:27:20.190 --> 00:27:23.179
you start correcting it.

00:27:23.179 --> 00:27:44.760
Now the new awareness that comes into you
is not something that can be just certified

00:27:44.760 --> 00:27:49.090
that, ‘Alright, now you are realized souls.

00:27:49.090 --> 00:27:52.330
Have a brand and go ahead.’

00:27:52.330 --> 00:27:55.510
It is not that way.

00:27:55.510 --> 00:28:09.700
But you become conscious of that awareness,
because for the first time, when the Kundalini

00:28:09.700 --> 00:28:17.380
pierces through this fontanelle bone area,
then you feel the cool breeze of the Holy

00:28:17.380 --> 00:28:18.909
Ghost coming in.

00:28:18.909 --> 00:28:24.840
In the Sanskrit language, Holy Ghost is called
as Adi Shakti.

00:28:24.840 --> 00:28:33.700
Most surprising is that, I don’t know why,
but in the Bible, Holy Ghost was not discussed

00:28:33.700 --> 00:28:34.700
much.

00:28:34.700 --> 00:28:49.610
Adi Shakti is the Holy Ghost, and about Adi
Shakti if you have 

00:28:49.610 --> 00:28:53.620
to learn, you have to go to Indian Scriptures.

00:28:53.620 --> 00:29:06.120
Even in the Old Testament they say Jews know
about it.

00:29:06.120 --> 00:29:17.760
Now this power, which is the All-Pervading
power of God, the power of His Love, becomes

00:29:17.760 --> 00:29:23.309
evident, because you start feeling it on your
fingers.

00:29:23.309 --> 00:29:34.019
And as you say in the English language, you
know, on your fingertips.

00:29:34.019 --> 00:29:38.049
Your hands start speaking.

00:29:38.049 --> 00:29:45.700
You can feel another personality, you can
put the hand towards another person, and you

00:29:45.700 --> 00:29:55.019
can see what are the centers catching, because
they are shown on this five, six and seven

00:29:55.019 --> 00:29:58.940
on the right, five, six and seven on the left.

00:29:58.940 --> 00:30:03.929
This is the emotional side, and the right
is the physical and the mental side.

00:30:03.929 --> 00:30:09.289
Now the doctors cannot deal with the psychosomatic,
or psychological things, and it’s a very

00:30:09.289 --> 00:30:12.509
big problem because there is only analysis
for you.

00:30:12.509 --> 00:30:22.139
Now, for a doctor it is important to know
both the sides of human beings, or I would

00:30:22.139 --> 00:30:26.379
say the three sides: the physical, the mental
and the emotional.

00:30:26.379 --> 00:30:37.289
But it is not so – he just knows part of
it, while a psychologist knows a part of it,

00:30:37.289 --> 00:30:44.149
and that’s how we cannot find out the reason
for the problems that exist within us.

00:30:44.149 --> 00:30:59.580
But when this Kundalini rises, She passes
through these six centers which are the milestones

00:30:59.580 --> 00:31:01.860
of our evolution, and thus integrates you
completely.

00:31:01.860 --> 00:31:06.179
So the first thing you receive is the integration.

00:31:06.179 --> 00:31:16.420
By that integration you are amazed that physically
you get cured.

00:31:16.420 --> 00:31:22.769
There has been a criticism about us in the
newspaper, that we have started curing people.

00:31:22.769 --> 00:31:34.909
Thank God we are not in America; there we
would have been arrested, because the doctors

00:31:34.909 --> 00:31:37.080
there do not allow anybody to cure anyone.

00:31:37.080 --> 00:31:38.440
But we do not cure.

00:31:38.440 --> 00:31:41.370
Automatically it happens: when the Kundalini
will rise, automatically it will happen that

00:31:41.370 --> 00:31:51.529
your whole being itself will become integrated
by which you will be healed.

00:31:51.529 --> 00:31:54.650
You will heal yourself, nobody else is going
to heal you.

00:31:54.650 --> 00:31:58.769
I don’t (know?) under law if you can charge
a person if he heals himself, but this will

00:31:58.769 --> 00:32:01.990
exactly happen that you will heal yourself,
and you will know how to heal yourself.

00:32:01.990 --> 00:32:02.990
But this is nothing.

00:32:02.990 --> 00:32:06.390
Is not only the physical side of it that happens
to you.

00:32:06.390 --> 00:32:09.029
Is just the minimum of minimums.

00:32:09.029 --> 00:32:15.130
But those people who (are?) suffering from
mental trouble also get healed.

00:32:15.130 --> 00:32:21.860
The third side of it is that physically you
are alright, mentally you are alright, and

00:32:21.860 --> 00:32:23.559
emotionally also, you are alright.

00:32:23.559 --> 00:32:29.690
Now there’s a very big confusion about mental
and emotional in English language.

00:32:29.690 --> 00:32:44.710
So if you have to say ‘mental’ as the
brain is concerned, then they mean to say

00:32:44.710 --> 00:32:49.820
that person who is mad is a mental case.

00:32:49.820 --> 00:32:54.860
Actually he’s a heart case, because he’s
working with his heart.

00:32:54.860 --> 00:33:01.130
He weeps, cries, but his head goes off, it’s
a balance.

00:33:01.130 --> 00:33:10.279
When he’s working with his head too much,
his heart goes off.

00:33:10.279 --> 00:33:13.889
That’s another balance of the nature.

00:33:13.889 --> 00:33:26.049
So if you have even the problem if you think
too much, some people are so mad that they

00:33:26.049 --> 00:33:35.659
go on thinking like mad, they cannot stop
their thinking, they think, think, think,

00:33:35.659 --> 00:33:39.200
think, and they’re thinking madness there,
but they cannot stop it.

00:33:39.200 --> 00:33:45.200
So here, when the Kundalini rises, onto this
point, you become thoughtlessly aware.

00:33:45.200 --> 00:33:50.720
You don’t have to think; you can stop your
thoughts.

00:33:50.720 --> 00:34:00.120
If you want to think you can think, if you
want to stop, you can stop.

00:34:00.120 --> 00:34:08.300
It is not necessary for you to think, and
that’s exactly what happens when the Kundalini

00:34:08.300 --> 00:34:13.290
rises here, that mentally you become absolutely
comfortable.

00:34:13.290 --> 00:34:19.810
Now this business of raising the Kundalini
is a business of God, and which cannot be

00:34:19.810 --> 00:34:20.810
sold.

00:34:20.810 --> 00:34:23.550
You cannot have a business on the human level.

00:34:23.550 --> 00:34:25.369
You cannot sell it.

00:34:25.369 --> 00:34:27.649
You just cannot do it.

00:34:27.649 --> 00:34:29.929
How it happens is automatically.

00:34:29.929 --> 00:34:31.389
By the grace of God it works out.

00:34:31.389 --> 00:34:36.119
You cannot sell anything that is the grace
of God.

00:34:36.119 --> 00:34:39.349
What is the value of that?

00:34:39.349 --> 00:34:49.020
On this point only many people discard Sahaja
Yoga because they think that it cannot be

00:34:49.020 --> 00:34:52.359
sold so it must be useless.

00:34:52.359 --> 00:34:58.770
It is so invaluable that you cannot pay for
it.

00:34:58.770 --> 00:35:10.830
Now the rising of the Kundalini has to take
place, first of all.

00:35:10.830 --> 00:35:18.290
(Could possibly be missing some lines here
on the recording..)

00:35:18.290 --> 00:35:19.290
…the Spirit.

00:35:19.290 --> 00:35:22.590
The Spirit is the one who is the master in
you.

00:35:22.590 --> 00:35:26.890
So you become your own master, you become
your own guru.

00:35:26.890 --> 00:35:37.160
Nobody has to tell you ‘do this’ or ‘do
that’; you are guided, because as soon as

00:35:37.160 --> 00:35:44.640
the Kundalini rises, you start feeling the
cool breeze in your hands.

00:35:44.640 --> 00:35:52.109
And these are giving you a new vibrations,
a new dimension by which you know whether

00:35:52.109 --> 00:35:53.830
to do this or not.

00:35:53.830 --> 00:35:56.721
For example, you want to do something; you
want to buy a book.

00:35:56.721 --> 00:36:02.400
You don’t have to decide about it: as soon
as you go near the book either it will give

00:36:02.400 --> 00:36:11.890
you cool breeze, or it may make you hot, or
it may little bit burn also if it’s a horrid

00:36:11.890 --> 00:36:17.510
one, and you don’t want to have that at
any cost, you want to have the cool breeze

00:36:17.510 --> 00:36:18.510
because you enjoy it.

00:36:18.510 --> 00:36:19.690
So you just give up.

00:36:19.690 --> 00:36:23.000
You just give up things without anybody telling
you, because your vibrations tell you.

00:36:23.000 --> 00:36:26.809
The spirit that has now shine in your attention,
tells you, and you start understanding, that

00:36:26.809 --> 00:36:37.000
now I have become my own guru, because your
guru is sitting inside you as the Spirit.

00:36:37.000 --> 00:36:40.160
It has not yet manifested in your attention
and that’s why you’re worried.

00:36:40.160 --> 00:36:48.280
But just it manifests, and once it manifests
you are amazed, that you yourself may have

00:36:48.280 --> 00:36:51.730
become a guru of yourself.

00:36:51.730 --> 00:37:00.660
You don’t need anybody else to tell you,
but you can do it yourself.

00:37:00.660 --> 00:37:04.000
You can find out yourself.

00:37:04.000 --> 00:37:14.010
Nobody has to give any explanation, or correction,
or anything, you just start improving yourself.

00:37:14.010 --> 00:37:23.920
Automatically it works, and little bit, if
you know, how to decode it, and how to work

00:37:23.920 --> 00:37:29.740
it out, your problems, you just manage it.

00:37:29.740 --> 00:37:31.790
You become yourself a guru.

00:37:31.790 --> 00:37:36.540
That’s the thing you have to be.

00:37:36.540 --> 00:37:40.540
Of course I told you, you cannot pay for it.

00:37:40.540 --> 00:37:44.020
It’s an insult even to think that you can
pay for it.

00:37:44.020 --> 00:37:51.089
Nobody can understand this; that this is complete
benevolence, is complete.

00:37:51.089 --> 00:37:55.270
It’s not mercenary act of benevolence, but
it is a complete, absolute benevolence, and

00:37:55.270 --> 00:37:56.480
for this benevolence you cannot pay.

00:37:56.480 --> 00:38:00.240
As soon as you pay for it, it is no more of
benevolence.

00:38:00.240 --> 00:38:05.460
And that’s why you cannot pay for it.

00:38:05.460 --> 00:38:10.710
You cannot work it out, it has to just work
out.

00:38:10.710 --> 00:38:20.609
Now, especially in the west, there is a problem
with people that they think, ‘Why should

00:38:20.609 --> 00:38:22.660
Mother do it?’.

00:38:22.660 --> 00:38:25.260
I tell you, it’s a thankless job.

00:38:25.260 --> 00:38:26.940
You cannot do it.

00:38:26.940 --> 00:38:33.200
If you can do it, I’ll be happy to retire.

00:38:33.200 --> 00:38:37.030
But you cannot do it.

00:38:37.030 --> 00:38:38.329
That’s the point (INAUDIBLE).

00:38:38.329 --> 00:38:40.760
This is my job, what am I to do?

00:38:40.760 --> 00:38:45.410
Supposing I am that, what am I to do now?

00:38:45.410 --> 00:38:52.930
If I have to do it, if I am supposed to do
it, then what should I do?

00:38:52.930 --> 00:39:04.329
I mean supposing you are posted as something;
you are a policeman, you have to do the policeman’s

00:39:04.329 --> 00:39:05.329
job.

00:39:05.329 --> 00:39:07.869
Now, how can you challenge it?

00:39:07.869 --> 00:39:10.400
He has to do it.

00:39:10.400 --> 00:39:19.300
As if you can say, I’m paid for it, or you
can say that this is my job.

00:39:19.300 --> 00:39:25.050
This I have to do, though I know it is very,
very troublesome.

00:39:25.050 --> 00:39:31.809
To get it done is not easy, it’s not very
easy.

00:39:31.809 --> 00:39:40.400
Everyone may not get realization, I cannot
guarantee that.

00:39:40.400 --> 00:39:53.359
I cannot say that you all will get the realization,
it’s a very difficult thing.

00:39:53.359 --> 00:39:58.109
Some people will just miss it for some time.

00:39:58.109 --> 00:40:04.450
There’s nothing to be worried about it;
it has to be corrected.

00:40:04.450 --> 00:40:07.910
It has to be redeemed, as they say.

00:40:07.910 --> 00:40:15.460
The Kundalini has to be brought up, if there
are centers catching they have to be cleared

00:40:15.460 --> 00:40:20.010
out, they have to be brought up, and we have
to have complete understanding and compassion

00:40:20.010 --> 00:40:26.140
about ourselves, and love for ourself and
respect for ourself.

00:40:26.140 --> 00:40:35.460
That if you have to become the light, then
we have to adjust and cooperate.

00:40:35.460 --> 00:40:43.720
Now the thing is that the ego part of it is
the strongest enemy of realization.

00:40:43.720 --> 00:40:45.150
I. I like it.

00:40:45.150 --> 00:40:47.579
I am this, I am that.

00:40:47.579 --> 00:40:56.480
When you say of ‘I, it is not yourself,
your spirit, but it is your ego that’s saying

00:40:56.480 --> 00:40:57.480
‘I’.

00:40:57.480 --> 00:41:04.920
When you become the spirit you don’t say
‘I’, but you say ‘it’.

00:41:04.920 --> 00:41:07.720
You talk in the third person.

00:41:07.720 --> 00:41:21.350
You say, ‘It is not coming up, it is not
working out, it is not’, in a third way.

00:41:21.350 --> 00:41:24.510
You never say, ‘I will raise the Kundalini’.

00:41:24.510 --> 00:41:29.040
What you will say: ‘the Kundalini is not
coming up.

00:41:29.040 --> 00:41:30.630
The Kundalini is not there.’

00:41:30.630 --> 00:41:39.460
In a third person you start talking, so that
you do not take any credit or discredit for

00:41:39.460 --> 00:41:40.460
it.

00:41:40.460 --> 00:41:52.520
Now, it is for you to observe it and see for
yourself.

00:41:52.520 --> 00:41:56.290
It depends on your power of observation.

00:41:56.290 --> 00:42:06.470
Whatever doctors may tell you, or anything,
you don’t have to believe those, because

00:42:06.470 --> 00:42:09.500
it depends on your own observation and sense
of penetration.

00:42:09.500 --> 00:42:24.299
Like I would say, I went to the Union Society
and the Chairman of the Union Society was

00:42:24.299 --> 00:42:25.740
82-year-old man.

00:42:25.740 --> 00:42:29.339
And he got his realization.

00:42:29.339 --> 00:42:38.690
And I told about Jung’s mistake why he missed
the point, which they understood very well.

00:42:38.690 --> 00:42:46.049
But then he got up, very humbly, and he says,
‘Mother, now you have learned our language,

00:42:46.049 --> 00:42:50.890
let us talk your language, let us learn your
language’.

00:42:50.890 --> 00:42:58.720
And then at the second meeting he says, ‘Now
I have observed - it’s not a question, but

00:42:58.720 --> 00:43:05.300
my observation, if it is true - that you don’t
believe in time.

00:43:05.300 --> 00:43:06.950
There’s no time.’

00:43:06.950 --> 00:43:09.770
Just you give it like that.

00:43:09.770 --> 00:43:13.640
That depends on your own observation.

00:43:13.640 --> 00:43:20.790
But I would not like to accept any ideas about
Me because I know it is terrible; sometimes

00:43:20.790 --> 00:43:22.380
it can act against.

00:43:22.380 --> 00:43:28.130
I mean, some people may just leave, you know,
they can’t bear it anymore.

00:43:28.130 --> 00:43:29.760
So that’s not the point.

00:43:29.760 --> 00:43:32.819
You have to see for yourself, observe yourself.

00:43:32.819 --> 00:43:41.270
There’s nothing to gain from you, at all
for Me, you cannot give Me anything, whatever

00:43:41.270 --> 00:43:42.690
you may try.

00:43:42.690 --> 00:43:45.790
There’s nothing to ask for.

00:43:45.790 --> 00:44:04.430
It is you who have to take something from
Me which you better have it.

00:44:04.430 --> 00:44:09.890
I’m like a cashier on the bank, see?

00:44:09.890 --> 00:44:14.200
You have got your cheques.

00:44:14.200 --> 00:44:17.440
Now, I have nothing to get from you.

00:44:17.440 --> 00:44:24.369
The cashier is paid for, alright, that’s
one point, is different, from the employer,

00:44:24.369 --> 00:44:26.170
but not by you.

00:44:26.170 --> 00:44:32.460
And what I have to do is to take your cheques
and cash it.

00:44:32.460 --> 00:44:37.250
Now, when you are in that position, will you
be angry with me for that?

00:44:37.250 --> 00:44:46.930
Will you say to your cashier, ‘Why are you
doing this to me?

00:44:46.930 --> 00:44:49.030
Why should I take money from you?’

00:44:49.030 --> 00:44:57.680
If that is intelligible, then we can see there
is some meeting point between us, and we can

00:44:57.680 --> 00:45:04.080
talk of realization then in a way that it
has to be done.

00:45:04.080 --> 00:45:11.530
You all have to have your key, your spirit,
that is within you.

00:45:11.530 --> 00:45:14.190
Perhaps I know that better than you.

00:45:14.190 --> 00:45:15.320
You know many things better than Me.

00:45:15.320 --> 00:45:20.020
I don’t know even how to use a plastic bag,
but I know how to open the Kundalini.

00:45:20.020 --> 00:45:27.250
I am so hopelessly bad at so many things which
are so trivial and simple which you can do

00:45:27.250 --> 00:45:30.990
just like that, I cannot do it.

00:45:30.990 --> 00:45:38.079
So it’s alright, so, I am also quite humble
about it, I don’t mind.

00:45:38.079 --> 00:45:44.110
I don’t know many things, but I know one
thing, is that you are the Spirit, and you

00:45:44.110 --> 00:45:50.020
have to become the Spirit, through the awakening
of your Kundalini.

00:45:50.020 --> 00:46:00.050
This is what a Mother can do, is to explain
to you, that come to the right conclusion,

00:46:00.050 --> 00:46:09.829
that you have to have it, it is within you,
and you have to get it.

00:46:09.829 --> 00:46:12.339
But I cannot force it on you.

00:46:12.339 --> 00:46:14.230
I cannot make you take it.

00:46:14.230 --> 00:46:17.470
Or else if you do not want to have it I just
can’t do it.

00:46:17.470 --> 00:46:18.470
It’s impossible.

