There’s no (hypnosis?)

00:46:19.530 --> 00:46:20.530
in it.

00:46:20.530 --> 00:46:27.250
It’s a happening that has to take place
with complete understanding of your freedom.

00:46:27.250 --> 00:46:36.770
I hope you will understand this new method,
that if you have to go to the roots, you have

00:46:36.770 --> 00:46:44.510
to become subtler than what you are, and to
become that subtler being, you have to become

00:46:44.510 --> 00:46:47.300
the Spirit, your Kundalini has to be awakened.

00:46:47.300 --> 00:46:59.170
Now, if you have any questions, you can ask
me, and there’s no need to be aggressive

00:46:59.170 --> 00:47:04.290
with me, because I have not come here to take
anything from you.

00:47:04.290 --> 00:47:10.280
But if you have any questions you can ask
me.

00:47:10.280 --> 00:47:19.079
One thing I must tell you: if you are going
to some other guru, or something, because

00:47:19.079 --> 00:47:28.470
I have seen also these people are going to
other gurus and I think these gurus feel threatened

00:47:28.470 --> 00:47:33.119
because I don’t take any money and they
feel threatened about it, whatever it is.

00:47:33.119 --> 00:47:38.609
If you are (registered/adjusted?) with any
guru or still attached to someone, you may

00:47:38.609 --> 00:47:44.000
go away, because I am not here to quarrel
with you for that.

00:47:44.000 --> 00:47:48.970
You can go away; it’s all your free choice.

00:47:48.970 --> 00:47:55.349
But if you want to become the Spirit, if you
want to have your realization, you’re welcome;

00:47:55.349 --> 00:47:58.750
I’ll be very happy to work it out.

00:47:58.750 --> 00:48:02.089
Now, let me have some questions if you have.

00:48:02.089 --> 00:48:03.089
Yes?

00:48:03.089 --> 00:48:04.130
(Inaudible question from audience.

00:48:04.130 --> 00:48:10.260
Yogi: What happens to your self-realization
when the body dies?

00:48:10.260 --> 00:48:13.630
What happens to your Kundalini and Spirit?)

00:48:13.630 --> 00:48:15.230
That is again futuristic.

00:48:15.230 --> 00:48:18.950
You be in the present, my child, alright?

00:48:18.950 --> 00:48:22.200
Now this is a very futuristic question.

00:48:22.200 --> 00:48:29.230
Now you’re not going to die, I can assure
you, for some time.

00:48:29.230 --> 00:48:31.920
So we’ll do it later on.

00:48:31.920 --> 00:48:36.030
Because why should you worry about your death
just now?

00:48:36.030 --> 00:48:38.710
I am talking of eternal life.

00:48:38.710 --> 00:48:42.289
Let’s (take?) it, be in the present, alright?

00:48:42.289 --> 00:48:46.960
It’s a good question, but why should you
worry about death?

00:48:46.960 --> 00:48:49.010
(Inaudible discussion in the audience.

00:48:49.010 --> 00:48:52.119
Yogi: Just, Mother’s given you the answer.

00:48:52.119 --> 00:48:53.260
Just leave it.)

00:48:53.260 --> 00:48:54.700
I have given you the answer.

00:48:54.700 --> 00:49:09.250
This is not the time to talk about it, it
requires a complete lecture, alright?

00:49:09.250 --> 00:49:13.690
I’ll tell you later on.

00:49:13.690 --> 00:49:16.589
I’ll write to you.

00:49:16.589 --> 00:49:22.260
You give me your address, I’ll write to
you.

00:49:22.260 --> 00:49:25.069
(Further inaudible discussion in the audience.

00:49:25.069 --> 00:49:27.130
Yogi: Next question, please.)

00:49:27.130 --> 00:49:32.030
Now don’t take others’ time, because I’m
not interested, now.

00:49:32.030 --> 00:49:37.030
Don’t be interested what happens to your
death, and what happens.

00:49:37.030 --> 00:49:42.839
That is not to be seen just now.

00:49:42.839 --> 00:49:46.690
Just now you get your realization; the first
step.

00:49:46.690 --> 00:49:51.690
That’s why Bhudda did not talk of God, even,
because he thought, he talks of God then people

00:49:51.690 --> 00:49:53.520
ask, ‘What is God?

00:49:53.520 --> 00:49:54.900
Where is He?

00:49:54.900 --> 00:49:57.190
Well, can I see Him?

00:49:57.190 --> 00:49:59.020
Can I meet Him?’.

00:49:59.020 --> 00:50:00.849
So he said, alright.

00:50:00.849 --> 00:50:02.809
Just take your self-realization, finished.

00:50:02.809 --> 00:50:04.670
Nothing more than that.

00:50:04.670 --> 00:50:07.000
(Further inaudible discussion in audience.)

00:50:07.000 --> 00:50:09.780
No, no, no, please sit down.

00:50:09.780 --> 00:50:13.500
You are from some other group, I think.

00:50:13.500 --> 00:50:15.490
Do you belong to some other group?

00:50:15.490 --> 00:50:16.859
(Inaudible response from audience).

00:50:16.859 --> 00:50:18.869
I know, I know that.

00:50:18.869 --> 00:50:20.770
No, please sit down.

00:50:20.770 --> 00:50:23.150
We don’t want you here.

00:50:23.150 --> 00:50:24.579
Please sit down.

00:50:24.579 --> 00:50:27.510
Now this is not the way to behave.

00:50:27.510 --> 00:50:35.020
We don’t go to your group, why don’t you
take your own hall and give a lecture there?

00:50:35.020 --> 00:50:40.010
If you belong to another group you don’t
come here.

00:50:40.010 --> 00:50:43.530
These people have been always troubling us
like this.

00:50:43.530 --> 00:50:45.099
This is too much.

00:50:45.099 --> 00:50:47.059
Why are you troubling us?

00:50:47.059 --> 00:50:49.410
What have we done to you?

00:50:49.410 --> 00:50:52.539
Why do you come here and trouble us?

00:50:52.539 --> 00:50:54.109
(Inaudible response from audience.)

00:50:54.109 --> 00:51:00.130
No, that’s not good, that’s not being
kind, and civil.

00:51:00.130 --> 00:51:04.740
You better learn these things, first of all.

00:51:04.740 --> 00:51:06.560
Please sit down.

00:51:06.560 --> 00:51:08.390
Please sit down.

00:51:08.390 --> 00:51:16.060
This is not the way to behave, to go to somebody’s
groups and, you see, I don’t go to these

00:51:16.060 --> 00:51:24.190
people, I don’t talk about these people,
why should you go to other peoples’?

00:51:24.190 --> 00:51:33.290
Go and learn from your guru and become whatever
you want to become, it’s alright.

00:51:33.290 --> 00:51:40.660
I’ve already told you, we shouldn’t trouble
somebody like this all the time.

00:51:40.660 --> 00:51:42.140
It’s not good.

00:51:42.140 --> 00:51:48.089
That’s why realization is needed; then you’ll
understand how to be gentle.

00:51:48.089 --> 00:51:52.460
They give big ideas; you become mokshas, you
become this, you have become this, and you,

00:51:52.460 --> 00:51:54.880
you go with those ideas.

00:51:54.880 --> 00:52:01.580
You don’t even have vibrations to feel what
you are; what your guru is.

00:52:01.580 --> 00:52:07.980
You don’t have any understanding, no discretion;
nothing.

00:52:07.980 --> 00:52:10.910
You go to a guru and he says, ‘Alright.

00:52:10.910 --> 00:52:16.119
Now you, you are going to go beyond everything’.

00:52:16.119 --> 00:52:17.520
You believe it.

00:52:17.520 --> 00:52:19.849
This is all ego pampering.

00:52:19.849 --> 00:52:23.859
If you want to live with it, go ahead.

00:52:23.859 --> 00:52:26.380
(Further inaudible discussion from audience.)

00:52:26.380 --> 00:52:33.839
You believe into whatever you believe it in
your own way, but whatever you believe has

00:52:33.839 --> 00:52:35.250
done no good to anyone.

00:52:35.250 --> 00:52:36.760
Has it done any good to anyone?

00:52:36.760 --> 00:52:40.049
You may believe into anything, so what?

00:52:40.049 --> 00:52:41.460
It’s not important.

00:52:41.460 --> 00:52:44.280
What have you done so far?

00:52:44.280 --> 00:52:47.579
What good have you done to anyone so far?

00:52:47.579 --> 00:52:50.119
(Further inaudible discussion from audience.)

00:52:50.119 --> 00:52:51.640
What’s he saying?

00:52:51.640 --> 00:52:54.170
(Yogi: Let’s leave it, please.)

00:52:54.170 --> 00:52:55.869
No, don’t do like that.

00:52:55.869 --> 00:52:56.869
(Yogi: Next question.)

00:52:56.869 --> 00:52:57.869
It’s not good.

00:52:57.869 --> 00:52:58.869
It’s not civil.

00:52:58.869 --> 00:53:00.200
No, no, no, no, no, no.

00:53:00.200 --> 00:53:02.750
You better join some politics, you’ll be
better there.

00:53:02.750 --> 00:53:03.920
(Audience laughter.)

00:53:03.920 --> 00:53:08.010
You are not meant for spiritual life.

00:53:08.010 --> 00:53:10.510
You go into some politics; you’ll be better
off.

00:53:10.510 --> 00:53:12.119
Now, let us have some other questions.

00:53:12.119 --> 00:53:13.950
(Yogi: If there are no questions, those few
people who want…)

00:53:13.950 --> 00:53:18.420
These are stupid people wasting their time,
I tell you, really, wasting their time, wasting

00:53:18.420 --> 00:53:19.420
our time.

00:53:19.420 --> 00:53:20.420
Done no good to anyone…

00:53:20.420 --> 00:53:21.750
(Inaudible question from audience.

00:53:21.750 --> 00:53:26.850
Yogi: If he gets self-realization, will it
interfere in any way with his normal functioning?)

00:53:26.850 --> 00:53:29.039
No, no, you will be very normal.

00:53:29.039 --> 00:53:30.960
(Shri Mataji and audience laughter.)

00:53:30.960 --> 00:53:31.960
You become extremely normal.

00:53:31.960 --> 00:53:35.920
You become so normal that you are amazed at
yourself.

00:53:35.920 --> 00:53:39.640
You see, all abnormalities drop out, first
of all.

00:53:39.640 --> 00:53:41.609
And secondly, you become so dynamic, absolutely
dynamic.

00:53:41.609 --> 00:53:46.069
We have people here who couldn’t do any
jobs, or they were depressed, this, that,

00:53:46.069 --> 00:53:51.140
but apart from that when they started doing
jobs they were surprised.

00:53:51.140 --> 00:53:56.099
The students who could not pass their exams
took first in the class, they had the highest

00:53:56.099 --> 00:53:57.099
marks.

00:53:57.099 --> 00:54:00.230
The people who could not concentrate become
well-known artists, well-known architects.

00:54:00.230 --> 00:54:16.059
We have so many Indian artists in India, especially,
who are very well-known artists but they had

00:54:16.059 --> 00:54:29.580
fallen prey to, say, alcohol, or something,
they have become great artists and now when

00:54:29.580 --> 00:54:35.070
they sing, you see, it’s so melodious, they
themselves now feel it that way.

00:54:35.070 --> 00:54:43.440
And on my birthday they came to sing, because
they said, ‘Mother, You have given us this

00:54:43.440 --> 00:54:45.529
new dimension in our music’.

00:54:45.529 --> 00:54:52.230
You become extremely creative, and very dynamic,
and you are not tired, because you get connected

00:54:52.230 --> 00:54:53.480
with the whole.

00:54:53.480 --> 00:54:54.480
(Yogi: Yes.

00:54:54.480 --> 00:54:55.990
Inaudible question from audience.

00:54:55.990 --> 00:54:58.500
Shri Mataji chuckles as She listens.)

00:54:58.500 --> 00:54:59.500
Thank you.

00:54:59.500 --> 00:55:03.109
(Further inaudible discussion from the same
questioner, a doctor.)

00:55:03.109 --> 00:55:10.340
Yes, doctor, I’m sorry to say it is so.

00:55:10.340 --> 00:55:12.183
It’s so many diseases can be cured, so many.

00:55:12.183 --> 00:55:20.090
I would not say all I would cover, like supposing
you have a cata, catarac, in the eye, and

00:55:20.090 --> 00:55:23.359
we cannot cure that, we have seen that.

00:55:23.359 --> 00:55:32.579
And also, things where something is dead in
the body, then you have to remove it, you

00:55:32.579 --> 00:55:35.099
see, and things like that.

00:55:35.099 --> 00:55:49.539
But I think if it is 
not in a very galloping state, if it is still

00:55:49.539 --> 00:55:55.260
there and if you do not interfere too much
with it, and do proper meditation the way

00:55:55.260 --> 00:56:03.680
it is to be done, you see these are only permutations
and combinations of these centers that we

00:56:03.680 --> 00:56:05.660
get into trouble.

00:56:05.660 --> 00:56:13.140
If you are in the center, you see, if you
are in the center, I mean, no less than Guru

00:56:13.140 --> 00:56:18.740
Nanak, Himself, has talked about it, absolutely,
and this is what work He has done.

00:56:18.740 --> 00:56:29.730
I’m doing His work, only, only thing is
that today is the time for, to give you the

00:56:29.730 --> 00:56:31.260
proof of what he said.

00:56:31.260 --> 00:56:39.980
So if these centers are kept normal, and if
the Kundalini starts flowing properly, then

00:56:39.980 --> 00:56:45.580
what happens is that you get connected with
that all-pervading power which is the life

00:56:45.580 --> 00:56:46.580
force itself.

00:56:46.580 --> 00:56:47.830
It’s not only Prana.

00:56:47.830 --> 00:56:53.960
It’s not only the right-sided thing which
we call the Prana, the white thing is, but

00:56:53.960 --> 00:56:58.150
also the emotional, and also the evolutionary
process, the sustenance.

00:56:58.150 --> 00:57:07.079
So it gives all the three forces within us
and if you know how to manipulate it and manifest

00:57:07.079 --> 00:57:11.480
it, you can work it out.

00:57:11.480 --> 00:57:15.710
And for you, especially, I would say, that
it is your heritage, itself, so for you it

00:57:15.710 --> 00:57:19.270
should be a great thing to understand it.

00:57:19.270 --> 00:57:28.560
But of course the patients who are absolutely
gone cases, and some patients, I would say,

00:57:28.560 --> 00:57:34.790
I must admit this, like Hitler, now, Hitler
I wouldn’t be able to cure, I’m sorry,

00:57:34.790 --> 00:57:40.980
because you must have some catch there also,
isn’t it?, with God.

00:57:40.980 --> 00:57:45.550
If you ask Me to cure Hitler or somebody like
that, it’s going to be difficult.

00:57:45.550 --> 00:57:57.010
But, people are normally good people, and
those who are good people, who lead a righteous

00:57:57.010 --> 00:58:07.270
life, not an aggressive life, and are of good
nature, can be easily cured.

00:58:07.270 --> 00:58:18.630
Once it happened that there was one doctor
Daetey; he brought Me a lady to be cured of

00:58:18.630 --> 00:58:28.349
her heart ailment, and she was very serious,
and he thought he, she, she may not be alright

00:58:28.349 --> 00:58:29.970
with Sahaja Yoga.

00:58:29.970 --> 00:58:36.109
But I cured her, but I told him that this
lady would not survive, within three days

00:58:36.109 --> 00:58:38.510
she is going to die.

00:58:38.510 --> 00:58:45.150
She was so much cured that he could not believe,
because every heartbeat was alright, everything

00:58:45.150 --> 00:58:46.150
was alright.

00:58:46.150 --> 00:58:50.980
He was surprised: I was saying that she is
going to die after three days.

00:58:50.980 --> 00:58:54.230
So he said, ‘How do you know, Mother?’.

00:58:54.230 --> 00:59:03.579
I said ‘I don’t know how do I know but
I know she is going to die’.

00:59:03.579 --> 00:59:11.240
Then I told him, ‘Doctor, you go and find
out the history of this woman, what sort of

00:59:11.240 --> 00:59:16.130
a woman she is, so then you will know what
I am saying.

00:59:16.130 --> 00:59:46.299
And he found out that she’s the woman because
of her, her daughter-in-law committed suicide,

00:59:46.299 --> 01:00:03.059
and her husband had become really mad; an
extremely aggressive woman and she has tortured

01:00:03.059 --> 01:00:22.920
all 
the people in the family.

01:00:22.920 --> 01:00:33.869
She had no love at all, and there was no need
for her to be blessed to that extent that

01:00:33.869 --> 01:00:38.410
she should get completely cured.

01:00:38.410 --> 01:00:44.230
Perhaps, I think her life was cut short was
good, and that’s how she could not survive,

01:00:44.230 --> 01:00:48.220
after that, and she died really after three
days.

01:00:48.220 --> 01:00:52.090
And the doctor Daetey was himself surprised.

01:00:52.090 --> 01:00:57.900
I told him himself, that, ‘You will get
a heart attack too, if you don’t take to

01:00:57.900 --> 01:01:03.720
Sahaja Yoga’, and he died of heart, because
his heart was catching, he wouldn’t believe,

01:01:03.720 --> 01:01:07.210
because he said, ‘It’s showing alright,
my x-ray’s alright’.

01:01:07.210 --> 01:01:08.770
I said, ‘It is not’.

01:01:08.770 --> 01:01:10.630
It is such a subtle thing.

01:01:10.630 --> 01:01:24.960
Before the disease starts, you see, you cannot
make out, but the disease starts at a point,

01:01:24.960 --> 01:01:33.220
when it is so subtle, that doctors also cannot
make it out.

01:01:33.220 --> 01:01:44.420
But in Sahaja Yoga you can.

01:01:44.420 --> 01:01:47.970
You catch on this finger.

01:01:47.970 --> 01:02:15.849
If you catch on this finger, that means there’s
some pressure on your heart.

01:02:15.849 --> 01:02:31.400
And if you’re catching on this finger it’s
better to pay attention to your heart immediately,

01:02:31.400 --> 01:02:42.789
and 
you carry the very simple thing, very simple,

01:02:42.789 --> 01:02:49.210
the mantra for heart attack is: ‘Mother
I am the Spirit’.

01:02:49.210 --> 01:02:52.779
Just (say/do) it.

01:02:52.779 --> 01:03:06.270
‘Mother I am the Spirit’.

01:03:06.270 --> 01:03:11.630
(Hindi translation), that’s all.

01:03:11.630 --> 01:03:24.150
If you say it three times you can get rid
of it.

01:03:24.150 --> 01:03:29.809
But, this mantra has to be siddh.

01:03:29.809 --> 01:03:47.650
Every Dick, Tom and Harry cannot give you
the mantra.

01:03:47.650 --> 01:03:56.059
Any person who is a realized soul can only
give you that.

01:03:56.059 --> 01:04:23.490
That is one thing very important.

01:04:23.490 --> 01:04:31.890
And Nanaka himself always talked about Satguru,
you see, because he found out that people

01:04:31.890 --> 01:04:35.720
used to talk about guru like Swami Ramdass
and all those talk of guru.

01:04:35.720 --> 01:04:40.589
But then he thought that it’s better to
call Satguru and guru as two things.

01:04:40.589 --> 01:04:46.440
Satguru is the one who has got realization,
and the one who calls himself as guru without

01:04:46.440 --> 01:04:50.160
realization talks big, ‘I, you, I’ll give
you this and I’ll give you that’, and

01:04:50.160 --> 01:04:53.660
just makes a big organization out of that,
is not a guru.

01:04:53.660 --> 01:05:00.180
So that is what it is, a person has to be
a realized soul, and he must know all the

01:05:00.180 --> 01:05:01.809
details about how to do it.

01:05:01.809 --> 01:05:06.349
Now, as if you are interested, I would like
to meet some of you doctors here, and I tell

01:05:06.349 --> 01:05:10.819
you all about it, details, and I can make
you master in no time, there’s no problem.

01:05:10.819 --> 01:05:15.940
But a Sahaja Yogi is a person who knows all
about Kundalini, he knows how to deal with

01:05:15.940 --> 01:05:17.650
it, how to work it out.

01:05:17.650 --> 01:05:22.510
Now he himself is a doctor, and he has cured
many people with Sahaja Yoga, and is a very

01:05:22.510 --> 01:05:24.750
simple thing, and which can work out.

01:05:24.750 --> 01:05:28.329
Thank God this country is a free country in
this respect, and that they have asked us

01:05:28.329 --> 01:05:32.109
to write to them about this method of Sahaja
Yoga; how we cure people.

01:05:32.109 --> 01:05:33.109
But that’s just the basics.

01:05:33.109 --> 01:05:35.329
That’s not so important.

01:05:35.329 --> 01:05:37.510
What is important is to become the spirit.

01:05:37.510 --> 01:05:41.250
(Inaudible question from same audience member.)

01:05:41.250 --> 01:05:43.740
Yes, by all means.

01:05:43.740 --> 01:05:44.980
Why not?

01:05:44.980 --> 01:05:48.590
I would love to have you for tea at my residence.

01:05:48.590 --> 01:05:50.114
You give your name and address and I’ll,
I’ll let you know.

01:05:50.114 --> 01:05:52.290
I thank you very much.

01:05:52.290 --> 01:05:54.940
Thank you very much doctor.

01:05:54.940 --> 01:05:55.940
Yes.

01:05:55.940 --> 01:05:57.059
(Yogi: Any more?

01:05:57.059 --> 01:05:58.059
Yes.)

01:05:58.059 --> 01:06:00.240
(Inaudible question from audience member.)

01:06:00.240 --> 01:06:02.359
What did he say?

01:06:02.359 --> 01:06:04.799
(Yogi: Sorry, could you say again?

01:06:04.799 --> 01:06:05.799
Ah.

01:06:05.799 --> 01:06:07.849
And you’re asking will it help.)

01:06:07.849 --> 01:06:08.849
Yes.

01:06:08.849 --> 01:06:09.920
(Yogi: His son has been very depressed.)

01:06:09.920 --> 01:06:11.510
Where do you live, in what part?

01:06:11.510 --> 01:06:12.650
(Inaudible response from audience member.)

01:06:12.650 --> 01:06:13.650
Alright.

01:06:13.650 --> 01:06:14.650
It’s not difficult; we have a center here.

