It’s very simple methods, they will tell
you; you have to have faith in yourself and

01:07:12.539 --> 01:07:15.819
you have to do it religiously, it will work
out.

01:07:15.819 --> 01:07:17.789
I promise it can be worked out.

01:07:17.789 --> 01:07:20.839
Now, behind you is sitting there some Mohan,
is sitting, just see that boy, sitting behind

01:07:20.839 --> 01:07:25.310
you, and he had been to some guru like that,
