01:07:25.310 --> 01:07:27.630
He was really, absolutely, out of mind.

01:07:27.630 --> 01:07:28.630
And now you won’t believe, he writes poetry
so beautifully, like, when I read it I think

01:07:28.630 --> 01:07:29.630
of Kabir, like that.

01:07:29.630 --> 01:07:30.630
He’s writing poetry now.

01:07:30.630 --> 01:07:31.630
So it’s something so different, you know?

01:07:31.630 --> 01:07:32.630
So, it can happen.

01:07:32.630 --> 01:07:33.630
You just bring the, you take the address and
bring the photograph of the boy, with his

01:07:33.630 --> 01:07:37.359
birth date and all that and give it to them,
