No, no, no.

01:08:26.200 --> 01:08:36.650
You see, it is Sahaja Samadhi.

01:08:36.650 --> 01:08:42.069
It is Sahaja.

01:08:42.069 --> 01:08:44.670
Sahaja has another meaning also; easy.

01:08:44.670 --> 01:08:51.509
That’s the quality of your mother, I should
say, has to be (easier/easiest?).

01:08:51.509 --> 01:08:53.759
Mother gives you birth, does she give you
any trouble?

01:08:53.759 --> 01:08:54.759
Nothing.

01:08:54.759 --> 01:08:56.900
She takes all the trouble, so you don’t
have to worry.

01:08:56.900 --> 01:09:00.870
Kundalini takes all the trouble within you,
you don’t have to do anything.

01:09:00.870 --> 01:09:04.130
So it’s very Sahaj, is absolutely Sahaj.

01:09:04.130 --> 01:09:05.130
It is absolutely spontaneous.

01:09:05.130 --> 01:09:07.980
It doesn’t give you trouble at all.

01:09:07.980 --> 01:09:12.140
It is absolutely easy, easy as possible.

01:09:12.140 --> 01:09:15.950
Has to be, because it is so vital.

01:09:15.950 --> 01:09:18.969
Whatever is not vital is like this, that guru
says, ‘Don’t eat this, don’t do that,

01:09:18.969 --> 01:09:20.969
stand on your heads, do this, do that’.

01:09:20.969 --> 01:09:22.810
That’s not the mother’s style.

01:09:22.810 --> 01:09:32.941
But the real gurus, also, they’re very strict,
no doubt, but the real gurus give you realization.

01:09:32.941 --> 01:09:33.950
That’s the first thing they do.

01:09:33.950 --> 01:09:37.310
They don’t tell you that, ‘I’ll take
you to mokshas, I’ll do this’, nothing

01:09:37.310 --> 01:09:38.310
of these big talks.

01:09:38.310 --> 01:09:42.140
They say that, ‘First of all you get your
realization’.

01:09:42.140 --> 01:09:47.700
Any other question, please.

01:09:47.700 --> 01:09:58.830
(Inaudible question from audience member and
general laughter.

01:09:58.830 --> 01:10:04.030
Yogi: Can you give some evidence of Your own
enlightenment?

01:10:04.030 --> 01:10:10.390
Shri Mataji laughs, more audience laughter.)

01:10:10.390 --> 01:10:11.690
What evidence you want?

01:10:11.690 --> 01:10:13.440
What evidence you understand?

01:10:13.440 --> 01:10:19.050
You see, the evidence is if your Kundalini
is awakened, then only you will understand.

01:10:19.050 --> 01:10:22.340
What Christ could not give evidence (so/to?)
you crucified him nicely.

01:10:22.340 --> 01:10:25.015
But I am going to give you the evidence, you
the evidence.

01:10:25.015 --> 01:10:26.015
I will give you.

01:10:26.015 --> 01:10:27.015
You sit down, you get your realization, then
you’ll get the evidence, alright?

01:10:27.015 --> 01:10:28.015
Once you get your realization you’ll get
the evidence, isn’t it?

01:10:28.015 --> 01:10:29.015
What is the evidence that the candle is enlightened?

01:10:29.015 --> 01:10:30.015
That it when you take it near an unlit, unlit…supposing
this is an enlightened candle, the evidence

01:10:30.015 --> 01:10:31.015
is that it can enlighten another candle, isn’t
it?

01:10:31.015 --> 01:10:32.015
That is the evidence.

01:10:32.015 --> 01:10:33.015
Now you sit down, first you, let’s see if
you get realization.

01:10:33.015 --> 01:10:34.015
That’s the evidence, alright?

01:10:34.015 --> 01:10:35.015
If you don’t get the realization, then the
evidence is that something wrong with you,

01:10:35.015 --> 01:10:36.015
because many will get it.

01:10:36.015 --> 01:10:37.015
It’s you who has to give Me the evidence,
not Me, because I don’t have, you see, these

01:10:37.015 --> 01:10:38.015
questions are alright for a person who’s
taking money from you, or taking anything

01:10:38.015 --> 01:10:39.015
from you, or I’m telling you anything, nothing,
I’m just saying, you take it.

01:10:39.015 --> 01:10:40.015
These questions are just other way around,
should be, isn’t it?

01:10:40.015 --> 01:10:41.015
It is you who has to give the evidence that
you have got it, not Me.

01:10:41.015 --> 01:10:42.015
Here at least there are 60% people who have
got it.

01:10:42.015 --> 01:10:43.015
60% people.

01:10:43.015 --> 01:10:44.015
So if you get it, thank your stars that you’ve
got it.

01:10:44.015 --> 01:10:45.015
If you don’t get it I’ll have to work
hard with you.

01:10:45.015 --> 01:10:46.015
(Yogi: Why don’t we all ask for it now.

01:10:46.015 --> 01:10:47.015
Just slip your shoes off, and put your hands
on your lap, put your hands out, and ask for

01:10:47.015 --> 01:10:48.015
it.

01:10:48.015 --> 01:10:49.015
Ask for it in your heart, that is.)

01:10:49.015 --> 01:10:50.015
I think all of you should get seated down,
first of all, properly.

01:10:50.015 --> 01:10:51.015
You see?

01:10:51.015 --> 01:10:52.015
There should be no (INAUDIBLE).

01:10:52.015 --> 01:10:53.015
Please be seated.

01:10:53.015 --> 01:10:54.015
There are some seats here.

01:10:54.015 --> 01:10:55.015
Come along.

01:10:55.015 --> 01:10:56.015
There are some seats here, also.

01:10:56.015 --> 01:10:57.015
There’s one thing I have to tell you, that
it is something that happens within yourself,

01:10:57.015 --> 01:10:58.015
and it is a very quick thing; it’s the split
of a second, when the Kundalini rises, just

01:10:58.015 --> 01:10:59.015
split of a second.

01:10:59.015 --> 01:11:00.015
But, if there is any obstruction, then it
takes some time, and I have seen, that say,

01:11:00.015 --> 01:11:01.015
in an Indian village, I have seen 6000 people
just get realization in the split of a second,

01:11:01.015 --> 01:11:02.015
but, the more we get sophisticated and modernized,
we get complicated.

01:11:02.015 --> 01:11:03.015
So, we have to, little bit, give some energy
to our different centers, and try to nourish

01:11:03.015 --> 01:11:04.015
it, so that the Kundalini is moving faster,
without any obstruction.

01:11:04.015 --> 01:11:05.015
To remove the obstruction, we have to work
it out in a very simple way, which I’ll

01:11:05.015 --> 01:11:06.015
tell you, that left hand you have to put like
this, which is the power of desire.

01:11:06.015 --> 01:11:07.015
So put the left hand like this.

01:11:07.015 --> 01:11:08.015
All these things I cannot explain in one,
one lecture, and it’s too much, also, like

01:11:08.015 --> 01:11:09.015
I would say that if you had to switch on then
you just pull the switch and the lights will

01:11:09.015 --> 01:11:10.015
be on.

01:11:10.015 --> 01:11:11.015
In the same way we can say put this left hand
straight like this, just like this, on your

01:11:11.015 --> 01:11:12.015
lap, very comfortably, and with the right
hand, I will say where to go.

01:11:12.015 --> 01:11:13.015
Now first of all, you must close your eyes,
and don’t open your eyes till I tell you.

01:11:13.015 --> 01:11:14.015
Take out your spectacles if possible, and…
it’s already going to deep I can’t keep

01:11:14.015 --> 01:11:15.015
my eyes open…

01:11:15.015 --> 01:11:16.015
now put the left hand towards Me and with
the right hand you have to move, so keep your

01:11:16.015 --> 01:11:17.015
eyes shut and also, if you can take out your
spectacles it’s better because you don’t

01:11:17.015 --> 01:11:18.015
have to see anything.

01:11:18.015 --> 01:11:19.015
Better, it’s good for the eyesight.

01:11:19.015 --> 01:11:20.530
So better take out your spectacles, and be
comfortable.

01:11:20.530 --> 01:11:23.880
There should be nothing tight anywhere in
the body, anywhere.

01:11:23.880 --> 01:11:27.389
Now, what you put your left hand towards Me,
and with the right hand, right hand, you put

01:11:27.389 --> 01:11:28.389
it on your heart on the left-hand side, to
begin with.

01:11:28.389 --> 01:11:29.389
It’s very important.

01:11:29.389 --> 01:11:31.890
Now, on the heart, we are putting it, first
of all, because we have to say that ‘Mother,

01:11:31.890 --> 01:11:32.890
I am the Spirit’.

01:11:32.890 --> 01:11:33.890
You can address Me as Shri Mataji, as Mother,
whatever.

01:11:33.890 --> 01:11:34.890
If it is easier for you to say Shri Mataji,
is alright, otherwise to make it easier you

01:11:34.890 --> 01:11:35.890
can call Me Mother.

01:11:35.890 --> 01:11:36.890
I am the Spirit.

01:11:36.890 --> 01:11:37.890
Everyone should try.

01:11:37.890 --> 01:11:38.890
Everyone should try.

01:11:38.890 --> 01:11:39.890
Or you can ask a question: ‘Am I the Spirit?’.

01:11:39.890 --> 01:11:40.890
Now, slowly take this side down on the left-hand
side of your stomach, left-hand side of your

01:11:40.890 --> 01:11:41.890
stomach, and press it hard.

01:11:41.890 --> 01:11:42.890
Left-hand side of your stomach.

01:11:42.890 --> 01:11:43.890
Don’t open your eyes.

01:11:43.890 --> 01:11:44.890
Put this right hand on the left-hand side
of your stomach, because there resides the

01:11:44.890 --> 01:11:45.890
principle of the Primordial master, of your
mastery.

01:11:45.890 --> 01:11:46.890
So here, you have to say, ten times, because
you have ten valencies.

01:11:46.890 --> 01:11:47.890
As human beings we have ten valencies, so
we have to say ten times: ‘Mother, I am

01:11:47.890 --> 01:11:48.890
my own master.

01:11:48.890 --> 01:11:49.890
I am my own guru’, to awaken within you
the Primordial master.

01:11:49.890 --> 01:11:50.890
‘I am my own guide.’

01:11:50.890 --> 01:11:51.890
With full confidence.

01:11:51.890 --> 01:11:52.890
Without any guilt, without any guilt.

01:11:52.890 --> 01:11:53.890
Without any guilt you have to say, ‘I’m
my own master’.

01:11:53.890 --> 01:11:54.890
This is one of the diseases in the west; to
feel guilty.

01:11:54.890 --> 01:11:55.890
At the present moment, your past is not there.

01:11:55.890 --> 01:11:56.890
You just worry, don’t worry about your past.

01:11:56.890 --> 01:11:57.890
You just say, ‘Mother, I am my own master’
with full confidence.

01:11:57.890 --> 01:11:58.890
Don’t feel guilty.

01:11:58.890 --> 01:11:59.890
(Long pause.)

01:11:59.890 --> 01:12:00.890
Please don’t feel guilty throughout.

01:12:00.890 --> 01:12:01.890
Please don’t feel guilty at all.

01:12:01.890 --> 01:12:02.890
And don’t count your sins but count your
blessings.

01:12:02.890 --> 01:12:03.890
Now raise this right hand, again, back to
the heart, with complete love and understanding

01:12:03.890 --> 01:12:04.890
about yourself, and full respect, because
you are at the epitome of the evolution.

01:12:04.890 --> 01:12:05.890
You must respect yourself.

01:12:05.890 --> 01:12:06.890
At this point, you have to say 12 times, ‘Mother
I am the Spirit’, because at this chakras,

01:12:06.890 --> 01:12:07.890
there are twelve sub-chakras, that’s why
it is to be said 12 times, or petals, sub-petals

01:12:07.890 --> 01:12:08.890
as they call it.

01:12:08.890 --> 01:12:09.890
Mother, I am the Spirit.

01:12:09.890 --> 01:12:10.890
Just say that.

01:12:10.890 --> 01:12:11.890
You are the Spirit, believe Me, you are.

01:12:11.890 --> 01:12:12.890
Just say that.

01:12:12.890 --> 01:12:13.890
(Long pause.

01:12:13.890 --> 01:12:14.890
Yogi tells Mother that he and/or the other
yogis present feel left vishuddi.)

01:12:14.890 --> 01:12:15.890
Now don’t feel guilty at that time.

01:12:15.890 --> 01:12:16.890
Don’t weep, or cry, don’t feel bad.

01:12:16.890 --> 01:12:17.890
Just say, ‘Mother, I am not guilty, I am
the Spirit’, with full confidence, you are.

01:12:17.890 --> 01:12:18.890
Don’t feel guilty.

01:12:18.890 --> 01:12:19.890
This feeling guilty causes angina, one part
of it, I tell you.

01:12:19.890 --> 01:12:20.890
Now, with that fear at least you’ll stop
feeling guilty.

01:12:20.890 --> 01:12:21.890
(Shri Mataji chuckles.

01:12:21.890 --> 01:12:22.890
She says to yogis), Hmm, better.

01:12:22.890 --> 01:12:23.890
Now put that right hand on the base of your
neck on the left-hand side, from the front.

01:12:23.890 --> 01:12:24.890
From the front.

01:12:24.890 --> 01:12:25.890
On the base, on the left-hand side.

01:12:25.890 --> 01:12:26.890
Base of your neck on the left-hand side, take
your hand in front, not from the back.

01:12:26.890 --> 01:12:27.890
Now press it hard, a little.

01:12:27.890 --> 01:12:28.890
Now this is the point, which catches very
badly, when you feel guilty.

01:12:28.890 --> 01:12:29.890
Now, just say, ‘Mother, I am not guilty’,
16 times.

01:12:29.890 --> 01:12:30.890
But I always say that if you have too much
of this fashion, of feeling guilty, then you

01:12:30.890 --> 01:12:31.890
may punish yourself by saying 35 times, or
108 times.

01:12:31.890 --> 01:12:32.890
Just laugh at yourself for feeling guilty;
that’s the best way.

01:12:32.890 --> 01:12:33.890
Do not condemn yourself.

01:12:33.890 --> 01:12:34.890
Say it 16 times.

01:12:34.890 --> 01:12:35.890
(Long pause.)

01:12:35.890 --> 01:12:36.890
Still you are feeling guilty.

01:12:36.890 --> 01:12:37.890
Now, put this hand on your forehead across,
without feeling guilty again.

01:12:37.890 --> 01:12:38.890
Throughout I have to say this because that’s
the main thing you’re catching, all the

01:12:38.890 --> 01:12:39.890
time, and at this point you have to say, ‘Mother,
I forgive everyone’.

01:12:39.890 --> 01:12:40.890
Just say that.

01:12:40.890 --> 01:12:41.890
Now, somebody would say that it’s very difficult
to forgive, and all that.

01:12:41.890 --> 01:12:42.890
It is all a myth.

01:12:42.890 --> 01:12:43.890
When you don’t forgive anyone, what do you
do?

01:12:43.890 --> 01:12:44.890
Nothing.

01:12:44.890 --> 01:12:45.890
You are actually cursing yourself, and torturing
yourself.

01:12:45.890 --> 01:12:46.890
So I forgive everyone.

01:12:46.890 --> 01:12:47.890
Mother, I forgive everyone.

01:12:47.890 --> 01:12:48.890
Forgive everyone.

01:12:48.890 --> 01:12:49.890
(Shri Mataji says mantras quietly.)

01:12:49.890 --> 01:12:50.890
Now put this hand at the back, on the backside
of your head, and pull it out a little bit.

01:12:50.890 --> 01:12:51.890
Press it a little bit.

01:12:51.890 --> 01:12:52.890
Now at this point, without feeling guilty,
again I say without feeling guilty, at all,

01:12:52.890 --> 01:12:53.890
just to say, that, ‘Oh Lord, Oh God, if
we have done any mistake, please forgive us’.

01:12:53.890 --> 01:12:54.890
But don’t feel guilty.

01:12:54.890 --> 01:12:55.890
(Pause.)

01:12:55.890 --> 01:12:56.890
At the back, just at the back of your head.

01:12:56.890 --> 01:12:57.890
(Longer pause as Mother speaks quietly aside
to the yogi/yogis.)

01:12:57.890 --> 01:12:58.890
Now, put this hand on top of your head, and
press it, on the fontanelle bone area, where

01:12:58.890 --> 01:12:59.890
you had a soft bone in your childhood, and
just press it, and rub it a little bit, and

01:12:59.890 --> 01:13:00.890
at this point as I said, I cannot cross your
freedom.

01:13:00.890 --> 01:13:01.890
You have to ask for it.

01:13:01.890 --> 01:13:02.890
You have to say, ‘Mother, I want my realization,
give me my realization’.

01:13:02.890 --> 01:13:03.890
Say it seven times here.

01:13:03.890 --> 01:13:04.890
Ask for it.

01:13:04.890 --> 01:13:05.890
You have to ask for it.

01:13:05.890 --> 01:13:06.890
You must know that the Divine is not going
to fall at your feet.

01:13:06.890 --> 01:13:07.890
You have to humble down, and ask for it, otherwise
it will not work out.

01:13:07.890 --> 01:13:08.890
(Pause; Mother speaks again, quietly, to yogis.)

01:13:08.890 --> 01:13:09.890
Now raise your hand, and see if there’s
a cool breeze coming in.

01:13:09.890 --> 01:13:10.890
Just not much, about five inches, six inches
higher, on top of your head.

01:13:10.890 --> 01:13:11.890
Now put down right hand, on your lap.

01:13:11.890 --> 01:13:12.890
Don’t open your eyes, please.

01:13:12.890 --> 01:13:13.890
Keep quiet.

01:13:13.890 --> 01:13:13.895
END
